  <bodyText><![CDATA[<h2>Multi-Centre Holidays in Europe</h2>
<p><img src="/media/13101938/adobestock_293414266.jpg" alt="multi-centre holidays" data-udi="umb://media/51dd97e3b0604f49b40c14d0bb3b9d0e" /></p>
<p>Step up your travel game with a multi-centre holiday. With the chance to discover and experience multiple destinations in one trip, you'll be able to walk your way through a variety of cultures, sights and adventures. </p>
<p>More destinations mean more unforgettable moments and we've chosen some of the most popular multi-centre combinations to help you get the most out of your time away.</p>
<div class="row">
<div class="col-md-12">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-grey c-card--generic-shadow ">
<div class="c-card_content c-section u-margin-top u-margin-bottom u-margin-left u-margin-right">
<h2 style="text-align: center;">How to Book Your Multi-Centre Holiday</h2>
<p style="text-align: center;">Simply decide which multi-centre you want to book and call us to arrange everything for you. Your travel from the UK, stays and transfers are all covered. Just pack your bags, choose your dream destination and let us take care of the small details.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="tel:01483791111" class="InfinityNumber c-btn">Call Us to Book Today</a></p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<p> </p>
<h2 style="text-align: center;">Our Multi-Centre Holidays</h2>
<p style="text-align: center;">Who says you can't have it all? Experience the very best of Europe's stunning landscapes, historic treasures, and culinary delights with a tailored multi-centre holiday.</p>
<div class="row">
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow u-text-center">
<div class="c-card__img"><img src="/media/13101941/adobestock_158306343.jpg" alt="Venice &amp; Lake Garda Multi-Centre Holiday" data-udi="umb://media/29304d4d34a6413180c69b4e65033a03" /></div>
<h3>Italy: Venice &amp; Lake Garda</h3>
<div class="c-card__content">
<p>Kick off your holiday in the magical streets of Venice, steeped in history and charm. After a couple of days, exploring the city's side streets, cafes and history, combine your Italian adventure with a visit to Lake Garda for serene waterside trails and sightseeing.</p>
<div class="c-card__cta-list c-card__cta-list--stacked"><a data-udi="umb://document/59c0b8bd5cea465e9207e6d534cc9558" href="/{localLink:umb://document/59c0b8bd5cea465e9207e6d534cc9558}" title="Venice &amp; Lake Garda" class="c-btn c-btn--secondary c-btn--mid c-btn--wide u-text-center" data-anchor="#">View Holiday</a></div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow u-text-center">
<div class="c-card__img"><img src="/media/13101943/hero-image_adobe-stock_537740604_grindlewaldpng.jpg" alt="Switzerland Multi-Centre Holiday" data-udi="umb://media/df786f3791014f88aa3b4f31645feafa" /></div>
<h3>Peaks of Switzerland: Grindelwald &amp; Zermatt</h3>
<div class="c-card__content">
<p>This is a perfect trip for ticking off the mega mountains in Switzerland - see the Matterhorn, Eiger, <span>Mönch and Jungfrau all in one trip. Admire 4,000 metre peaks, visit the glacier palaces and explore exciting alpine trails.</span></p>
</div>
<div class="c-card__cta-list c-card__cta-list--stacked"><a href="#" class="c-btn c-btn--secondary c-btn--mid c-btn--wide u-text-center">View Holiday</a></div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="row">
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow u-text-center">
<div class="c-card__img"><img src="/media/13101944/talloires-lake-anncey-adobestock_431501814.jpg" alt="France Multi-Centre Holiday" data-udi="umb://media/801b0ae42fd6488985480fe296d11470" /></div>
<h3>France: Chamonix &amp; Lake Annecy</h3>
<div class="c-card__content">
<p>Combine adventure in Chamonix with tranquility at Lake Annecy for the ultimate holiday. Chamonix, the adventure capital, buzzes with activities. Lake Annecy offers tranquility with lakeside strolls, bike rides and charming old town to explore.</p>
<div class="c-card__cta-list c-card__cta-list--stacked"><a href="#" class="c-btn c-btn--secondary c-btn--mid c-btn--wide u-text-center">View Holiday</a></div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow u-text-center">
<div class="c-card__img"><img src="/media/13101945/adobestock_220959569.jpg" alt="Slovenia multi-centre holiday" data-udi="umb://media/dbe105855892460eb5034b1892863984" /></div>
<h3>Slovenia: Julian Alps</h3>
<div class="c-card__content">
<p>Unlock the beauty of Slovenia with this trip along the Julian Alps. Think picture-perfect landscapes, nature-filled valleys and pretty towns and villages. Come for the views, stay for the charm and leave with a lifetime of memories.</p>
</div>
<div class="c-card__cta-list c-card__cta-list--stacked"><a href="#" class="c-btn c-btn--secondary c-btn--mid c-btn--wide u-text-center">View Holiday</a></div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<h2 style="text-align: left;">Travel With Confidence</h2>
<p style="text-align: left;">When you choose an Inghams holiday, you can travel with confidence. We’re here to take the stress out of travelling. We’ve put extra measures in place for your peace of mind. We’ll help keep both you and your money safe.</p>
<p><img style="width: 916px; height: 231px; float: left;" src="/media/13095389/inghams-in-safe-hands-charcoal.png?width=916&amp;height=231&amp;mode=max" alt="in safe hands" data-udi="umb://media/afba17a916e84fcc848acce5dda4f9c4" /></p>
<p><strong>Terms and Conditions</strong></p>
<p style="text-align: left;">**<span>Up to two guided walks per week are included in the following resorts: </span><a data-udi="umb://document/594483304a5f4b47844b444df2c9d975" href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/austria/austrian-tyrol/mayrhofen" title="Mayrhofen">Mayrhofen</a><span>, <a data-udi="umb://document/a71713291d5d4220aea1b806f34cd053" href="/{localLink:umb://document/a71713291d5d4220aea1b806f34cd053}" title="Seefeld">Seefeld</a>, </span><a data-udi="umb://document/ab49d5977a794ec7952da3e3d5adf48b" href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/austria/saalbach-hinterglemm" title="Saalbach &amp; Hinterglemm">Saalbach &amp; Hinterglemm</a><span>, </span><a data-udi="umb://document/2735e2389f7c411cb3061226ce7548d1" href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/france/chamonix" title="Chamonix">Chamonix</a><span>, </span><a data-udi="umb://document/a95b5199e8e04283bf8eeeabb42715fc" href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/france/morzine" title="Morzine">Morzine</a><span>, </span><a data-udi="umb://document/604dbba59ac64320ab6e9f1e89231a4c" href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/italy/lake-garda/limone" title="Limone">Limone</a><span>, <a data-udi="umb://document/c5c478381e04431da3f69d8364215ae7" href="/{localLink:umb://document/c5c478381e04431da3f69d8364215ae7}" title="Merano">Merano</a>,<a data-udi="umb://document/4c9fc09241f14e3c80acb89b5c9226dd" href="/{localLink:umb://document/4c9fc09241f14e3c80acb89b5c9226dd}" title="Selva"> Selva</a>, <a data-udi="umb://document/b45a359445114107972cbb2b00be85ae" href="/{localLink:umb://document/b45a359445114107972cbb2b00be85ae}" title="Champoluc" data-anchor="#">Champoluc</a>, <a data-udi="umb://document/de185d9ae756482295e4f069ba3a7aaf" href="/{localLink:umb://document/de185d9ae756482295e4f069ba3a7aaf}" title="Cervinia">Cervinia</a>, </span><a data-udi="umb://document/9b6cf6eac79541f5850e141e41a071ab" href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/slovenia/kranjska-gora" title="Kranjska Gora">Kranjska Gora</a><span>, </span><a data-udi="umb://document/0fe9200934b24cd49d20e1cea080f5da" href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/switzerland/bernese-oberland/grindelwald" title="Grindelwald">Grindelwald</a><span>, </span><a data-udi="umb://document/dd4c4793225641fcb24c0918a33714b3" href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/switzerland/bernese-oberland/wengen" title="Wengen">Wengen</a>, <a data-udi="umb://document/2e09d5bd5fae466db4b3c37d49150722" href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/switzerland/zermatt" title="Zermatt">Zermatt, </a><a data-udi="umb://document/cad35d37f73d435087041e35025d1da8" href="/{localLink:umb://document/cad35d37f73d435087041e35025d1da8}" title="Funchal">Funchal</a> and <a data-udi="umb://document/f6d745a0efdf44b5b28bcd4bee55dbb1" href="/{localLink:umb://document/f6d745a0efdf44b5b28bcd4bee55dbb1}" title="Canico">Caniço</a><span>. </span><span>All walks are subject to availability of local guides, weather conditions and maximum numbers. Where we cannot confirm your preferred option in resort, we will endeavour to offer an alternative subject to the above conditions. </span></p>
</div>]]></bodyText>
